tz.com/israel-news/2024-03-13/ty-article/.premium/west-bank-police-chief-most-complaints-of-settler-violence-are-false-filed-by-anarchists/0000018e-34cf-d5ad-addf-7cdff2310000</guid></item><item><title>“不可逆转的损害”：以色列火山研究所负责人抗议预算削减计划</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</link><description>火山研究所代理所长什穆埃尔·阿苏林 (Shmuel Assouline) 表示，由于提议的削减，该机构已暂停其活动，他警告说，这将导致该研究所关闭、诉讼和损害、正在申请的专利被取消以及其所拥有的知识产权的损失。国家</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 21:24:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/irreversible-damage-heads-of-israels-volcani-institute-protest-planned-budget-cuts/0000018e-342c-d5ad-addf-7c3d53b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列警方在东耶路撒冷射杀一名向他们发射烟花的 13 岁青少年</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</link><description>据难民营一名居民称，烟花并非针对军官，也不会对他们构成威胁。国家安全部长伊塔马尔·本-格维尔在回应这一事件时表示，他向警察对事件的处理“致敬”。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 20:35:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israeli-police-fatally-shot-a-13-year-old-who-launched-fireworks-at-them-in-east-jerusalem/0000018e-3457-da0e-a78f-fc7f43e80000</guid></item><item><title>新的加沙战争是拜登和内塔尼亚胡之间的</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-biden-and-netanyahu-conveniently-blame-each-other-for-their-gaza-war-failures/0000018e-33e4-d9f7-a5ee-f7ef84670000</link><description>传统观点认为，比比与拜登关系的恶化对两位领导人来说都是一个糟糕的发展。但真的是这样吗？在每种情况下，爆发相互批评和指责也是有好处的</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:46:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-03-12/ty-article/.highlight/how-biden-and-netanyahu-conveniently-blame-each-other-for-their-gaza-war-failures/0000018e-33e4-d9f7-a5ee-f7ef84670000</guid></item><item><title>希伯来大学停职否认哈马斯性暴力、指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的巴勒斯坦学者</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-suspends-palestinian-scholar-who-denied-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018e-3350-d5ad-addf-7f5130b60000</link><description>Nadera Shalhoub-Kevorkian教授分发了一份指责以色列在加沙实施种族灭绝的请愿书，她被要求离职但遭到拒绝，导致她被大学停职。该大学领导层对她的言论和活动表示“遗憾和羞耻”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:32:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/hebrew-university-suspends-palestinian-scholar-who-denied-hamas-sexual-violence/0000018e-3350-d5ad-addf-7f5130b60000</guid></item><item><title>美国《全球威胁报告》向以色列和内塔尼亚胡发出了严厉的信息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/u-s-worldwide-threats-report-says-what-biden-wont-about-gaza-war-and-netanyahu/0000018e-3379-de79-a78f-337d9a640000</link><description>国家情报总监的年度报告应该让人们对美国认为以色列对哈马斯的战争执行得有多好，以及对内塔尼亚胡政府的生存能力的看法毫无疑问。</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 19:00:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/u-s-worldwide-threats-report-says-what-biden-wont-about-gaza-war-and-netanyahu/0000018e-3379-de79-a78f-337d9a640000</guid></item><item><title>萨尔解散与甘茨的联盟，要求在加沙政策发生冲突时加入战时内阁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/saar-dissolves-alliance-with-gantz-demands-joining-war-cabinet-amid-clash-on-gaza-policy/0000018e-33eb-de79-a78f-33ef1da60000</link><description>萨尔引用了加沙五人战时内阁领导的政策来证明自己的决定是正确的。他呼吁加大对哈马斯的军事压力，暗示与中间派部长甘茨和艾森科特的立场存在分歧</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 18:54:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/saar-dissolves-alliance-with-gantz-demands-joining-war-cabinet-amid-clash-on-gaza-policy/0000018e-33eb-de79-a78f-33ef1da60000</guid></item><item><title>无名，戴着镣铐：以色列道德委员会审查加沙被拘留者的医疗情况</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/nameless-shackled-blindfolded-medical-treatment-of-detainees-from-gaza-examined/0000018e-327a-d5ad-addf-7e7bca660000</link><description>人权医生组织称以色列军事医疗院的条件——病人一直被戴上镣铐并蒙住眼睛——是“酷刑”</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:35:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/nameless-shackled-blindfolded-medical-treatment-of-detainees-from-gaza-examined/0000018e-327a-d5ad-addf-7e7bca660000</guid></item><item><title>新研究显示，可可出人意料地以惊人的速度征服了史前美洲</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cocoa-always-was-though-not-sure-always-will-be/0000018e-3322-d606-a5ff-7fb706420000</link><description>可可豆于 5,300 多年前在亚马逊地区被驯化，突然之间，杂交品种在整个南美洲北部和中美洲涌现</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:10:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/science/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/cocoa-always-was-though-not-sure-always-will-be/0000018e-3322-d606-a5ff-7fb706420000</guid></item><item><title>应德国要求，以色列将68名巴勒斯坦孤儿从拉法暂时撤离至约旦河西岸</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israel-temporarily-evacuates-68-orphans-from-rafah-to-west-bank-at-germanys-request/0000018e-3396-da0e-a78f-ffbeccf30000</link><description>德国驻特拉维夫大使馆表示，疏散的目的是立即使孩子们脱离“严重”危险，并且是暂时的，并不是永久搬迁。以色列国防军是在以色列政府的指示下进行此次行动的</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:08:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/israel-temporarily-evacuates-68-orphans-from-rafah-to-west-bank-at-germanys-request/0000018e-3396-da0e-a78f-ffbeccf30000</guid></item><item><title>战争中的以色列：您需要了解的信息 – 第 158 天</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-158/0000018e-337e-da0e-a78f-ff7e55a60001</link><description>多哈和开罗的停火谈判仍在继续，但卡塔尔外交部表示，“情况很复杂” ■ 黎巴嫩向以色列北部发射了 100 多枚火箭弹 ■ 据报道，拜登正在考虑对以色列提供进一步的军事援助，条件是这些援助是否会携带在加沙拉法发动大规模攻势 ■ 战争开始 158 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 17:00:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-what-you-need-to-know-day-158/0000018e-337e-da0e-a78f-ff7e55a60001</guid></item><item><title>他们的亲人在哈马斯囚禁期间被杀。他们为拯救他人的生命而战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-loved-ones-were-killed-in-captivity-they-call-to-save-others/0000018e-2f41-dcb3-a58f-efc5ddf90000</link><description>他们被绑架的亲属在加沙被杀。但只要还有其他以色列人仍被囚禁，他们的战斗就没有结束</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:45:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/their-loved-ones-were-killed-in-captivity-they-call-to-save-others/0000018e-2f41-dcb3-a58f-efc5ddf90000</guid></item><item><title>以色列批准载有200吨食品的援助船从塞浦路斯起航前往加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/aid-ship-with-200-tons-of-food-sets-sail-from-cyprus-to-gaza-after-israels-approval/0000018e-3338-d5ad-addf-7f3918220000</link><description>通过海运运送食物的努力突显了国际社会对人道主义援助卡车系统的不满，该系统导致加沙北部受到严重忽视。这艘船由 Open Arms 和 World Central Kitchen 组织，预计两三天内抵达加沙海岸</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 16:28:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/aid-ship-with-200-tons-of-food-sets-sail-from-cyprus-to-gaza-after-israels-approval/0000018e-3338-d5ad-addf-7f3918220000</guid></item><item><title>“如果以色列要这样对待人民，那么他们制定回归法还有什么意义呢？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/whats-the-point-of-having-a-law-of-return-if-theyre-going-to-treat-people-like-this/0000018e-2d0d-dbcf-abee-3ddd4d2d0000</link><description>在发给每个前往以色列回返的人的表格上诚实地回答一个人的心理健康史，有时会让移民走上侵入性询问和长期拖延的道路。一名女性的案例终于可以解决这个问题</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:54:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article-magazine/.premium/whats-the-point-of-having-a-law-of-return-if-theyre-going-to-treat-people-like-this/0000018e-2d0d-dbcf-abee-3ddd4d2d0000</guid></item><item><title>非政府组织起诉丹麦向以色列出售武器，并援引加沙“潜在的种族灭绝”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-12/ty-article/ngos-sue-denmark-over-arms-sales-to-israel-cite-potential-genocide-in-gaza/0000018e-3316-d606-a5ff-7fb760a30000</link><description>参与诉讼的组织之一的秘书长表示，政客们没有采取行动阻止“加沙潜在的种族灭绝”。上个月，荷兰法院下令荷兰禁止向以色列出口所有 F-35 战斗机零部件</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 15:17:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2024-03-12/ty-article/ngos-sue-denmark-over-arms-sales-to-israel-cite-potential-genocide-in-gaza/0000018e-3316-d606-a5ff-7fb760a30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩深处的真主党据点； 100枚火箭弹袭击以色列北部</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/idf-strikes-hezbollah-stronghold-deep-in-lebanon-100-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/0000018e-3263-df45-afaf-3f7775df0000</link><description>以色列战机袭击了距以色列北部边境一百多公里的巴勒贝克的真主党目标后，真主党向戈兰高地发射了战争中最大规模的火箭弹之一</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:49:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-12/ty-article/idf-strikes-hezbollah-stronghold-deep-in-lebanon-100-rockets-fired-at-northern-israel/0000018e-3263-df45-afaf-3f7775df0000</guid></item><item><title>为什么以色列的新民族主义犹太教不关心加沙的人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israels-new-nationalistic-judaism-doesnt-care-about-the-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-32d0-d5ad-addf-7ed15b390000</link><description>对于以色列不断崛起的沙文主义、救世主宗教右翼来说，加沙战争是为了恢复自豪感和投射权力。哈马斯扣押的绝望人质与他们的叙述不符</description><pubDate>Tue, 12 Mar 2024 14:42:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-12/ty-article-opinion/.premium/why-israels-new-nationalistic-judaism-doesnt-care-about-the-hostages-in-gaza/0000018e-32d0-d5ad-addf-7ed15b390000</guid></it